name: $createPlayer
description: Creates a new music player in the given guild.

args.name: Guild ID
args.description: The ID of the guild to create the player to.

args.name: Voice ID
args.description: The voice channel to connect to.

args.name: Text ID
args.description: The text channel to send messages to.

name: $destroyPlayer
description: Destroys a music player in the given guild.

args.name: Guild ID
args.description: The ID of the guild to create the player to.

name: $hasPlayer
description: Check whether the given guild has a player created.

args.name: Guild ID
args.description: The ID of the guild to create the player to.

name: $playerElapsedTime
description: Returns the elapsed time of the current song in milliseconds.

name: $playerQueueTime
description: Returns the total duration of all tracks in the player queue in milliseconds.

name: $playerTextID
description: gets the players text channel id.

args.name: Guild ID
args.description: The ID of the guild get the player ID from.

name: $addTrack
description: Adds a track into the guild player to listen to.

args.name: Guild ID
args.description: The ID of the guild to create the player to.
